{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"textHomeStatus":"Clear","voice":"vo_char_3056_00_01","textHome":"僕の名は水樹塁。数千年前の異世界大戦を勝\n利に導いた伝説の覇王の生まれ変わりなん\nだ。おっと、僕は“奴ら”から呪いを受け\nている。だから僕に触るのはやめるんだ。\n君の存在を「なかった」ことにされたくな\nければね。“奴ら”、この世界でも元気に\nしてるようだね"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"id":305600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305600,"motion":1}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"textHomeStatus":"Clear","voice":"vo_char_3056_00_17","textHome":"中二病になったのは…確かに「終約聖書」の\nせいだけど…で、でも出会ったことに後悔\nはないよ…。だって、あれから毎日、楽し\nいし…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"id":305600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":305600,"motion":300}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"textHomeStatus":"Clear","voice":"vo_char_3056_00_18","textHome":"みんな「終約聖書」のこと中二中二って叩く\nけど…、すごいじゃん…。あんな設定、普\n通は思いつかないよ…。私が、レビュー書\nかないと…！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":305600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305600,"motion":100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305600,"moti